data.description: Waterfront Recently RENOVATED kitchen and master bath on corner and waterfront lot! Downstairs has a guest room with an on-suite private full bath. Upstairs holds four remaining bedrooms to include master and two full baths. New kitchen expansion with upgraded cabinets and granite, glass backsplash, large custom sink with built in soap dispenser and push button disposal. Stainless-steel appliances added to kitchen to include a quiet Bosch dishwasher. Master bath has floor to ceiling tile, frameless glass shower door for your walk-in and deep soaker tub, most bathrooms have granite counter tops. NEW carpets in bedrooms and new washable paint in a neutral gray throughout.
